destiny ( arabic : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , translit . &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is a 1997 &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; historical drama film directed by youssef chahine . it was screened out of competition at the 1997 cannes film festival . the film was selected as the egyptian entry for the best foreign language film at the 70th academy awards , but was not accepted as a nominee . the film is about &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , a 12th-century philosopher from andalusia who would be known as the most important commentator on aristotle .